  m_text: Through BukSU Insight, these real-life campus procedures are transformed
    into interactive missions and gameplay. By completing in-game tasks, players
    learn how to navigate the university, locate offices, and understand important
    student requirements. This approach makes orientation more engaging, effective,
    and accessible, helping students feel more confident and prepared as they begin
    their journey at Bukidnon State University.
