  m_text: "Players choose and control their own avatar as they complete the game\u2019s
    main objectives and explore the entire campus. By interacting with people, gathering
    information, and navigating the environment, players gain a better understanding
    of university procedures and campus life.\n\nTake your time to explore, interact,
    and immerse yourself in the simulated world of BukSU Insight."
